author: Eli the Computer Guy
description:
RSVP for Classes at - http://www.SiliconDojo.com

Support Classes at - https://donorbox.org/etcg
LinkedIn at - https://www.linkedin.com/in/eli-etherton-a15362211/

Martin Lehner is the Owner of Tangerine Technology an MSP (Managed Service Provider) and a Cybersecurity Professional in the Canadian Yukon. He has decades of experience as a tech professional and can talk about the current hiring environment and what employers look for.

https://www.linkedin.com/in/martinlehner/
https://www.tangerinetechnology.is

We will discuss what the current landscape looks like for MSP's, discuss current conditions for Cybersecurity and get an idea of what the view of a Canadian tech Business owner is in regards to the current state of relations with the United States.
title: Martin Lehner Owner of Tangerine Technology (Canadian MSP)
